---
// Spaced repetition explainer with a forgetting-curve visual.
---
<section class="srs" id="srs">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="srs__card">
      <div class="srs__copy">
        <span class="srs__eyebrow">📚 Memory science</span>
        <h2 class="srs__title">Spaced repetition: you remember it until&nbsp;exam day</h2>
        <p class="srs__text">When you cram, you forget it in a few days. The app brings back each term and question just before you forget it - the best moment to review. By exam day you do not just feel ready, you really remember.</p>
        <ul class="srs__features">
          <li class="srs__feature">
            <span class="srs__icon">🧠</span>
            <span class="srs__feature-body">
              <span class="srs__feature-title">Active recall</span>
              <span class="srs__feature-sub">Remember it, do not just reread</span>
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="srs__feature">
            <span class="srs__icon">⏰</span>
            <span class="srs__feature-body">
              <span class="srs__feature-title">Right timing</span>
              <span class="srs__feature-sub">Review just before you forget</span>
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="srs__feature">
            <span class="srs__icon">📈</span>
            <span class="srs__feature-body">
              <span class="srs__feature-title">Long-term memory</span>
              <span class="srs__feature-sub">Locked in by exam day</span>
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <figure class="srs__viz">
        <svg class="srs__chart" viewBox="0 0 560 300" role="img" aria-label="Forgetting curve: spaced review keeps memory high while cramming fades">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="srsArea" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#34D399" stop-opacity="0.28"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#34D399" stop-opacity="0"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>

          <!-- gridlines -->
          <g stroke="#eef2f1" stroke-width="1">
            <line x1="48" y1="46" x2="540" y2="46"/>
            <line x1="48" y1="148" x2="540" y2="148"/>
            <line x1="48" y1="250" x2="540" y2="250"/>
          </g>

          <!-- y axis caption -->
          <text x="40" y="50" class="srs__axis" text-anchor="end">100%</text>
          <text x="40" y="254" class="srs__axis" text-anchor="end">0%</text>

          <!-- spaced retention area -->
          <path d="M60,46 C95,46 120,150 150,150 L150,46 C200,46 230,124 260,124 L260,46 C320,46 355,104 390,104 L390,46 C450,46 495,86 530,86 L530,250 L60,250 Z" fill="url(#srsArea)"/>

          <!-- cramming curve -->
          <path d="M60,46 C140,140 270,212 530,238" fill="none" stroke="#fca5a5" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="2 8"/>

          <!-- spaced retention curve -->
          <path d="M60,46 C95,46 120,150 150,150 L150,46 C200,46 230,124 260,124 L260,46 C320,46 355,104 390,104 L390,46 C450,46 495,86 530,86" fill="none" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="3.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>

          <!-- review markers -->
          <g>
            <circle cx="150" cy="46" r="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="3"/>
            <circle cx="260" cy="46" r="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="3"/>
            <circle cx="390" cy="46" r="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="3"/>
          </g>

          <!-- x axis day labels -->
          <g class="srs__axis" text-anchor="middle">
            <text x="60" y="272">Learn</text>
            <text x="150" y="272">Day 1</text>
            <text x="260" y="272">Day 3</text>
            <text x="390" y="272">Day 7</text>
            <text x="530" y="272">Day 16</text>
          </g>
        </svg>
        <figcaption class="srs__legend">
          <span class="srs__legend-item srs__legend-item--good"><span class="srs__legend-dot"></span>With spaced review</span>
          <span class="srs__legend-item srs__legend-item--bad"><span class="srs__legend-dot"></span>Cramming</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
